Output static/videos/loop-gemini.mp4
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 800
Set Height 500
Set Padding 24
Set Framerate 30
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Hide
Type "export PS1='> '"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "aeo-recording-gemini"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 75000ms
